Will you shop blind with me??

So there’s this company…

They are called @TwoBlindBrothers and I love them and everything that they stand for. They are on a mission to cure blindness. So I’ve partnered with them and I’m doing a #ShopBlindChallenge (unboxing).

They have this mystery box that they send you and it’s hand-picked everything! You don’t get to see the product pictures or anything before, so it’s SUPER FUN, mysterious and it’s for a good cause, because 100% of the profits go to help with research for the blind. AMAZING. 🥰

After the unboxing I was completely AMAZED! #TwoBlindBrothers  WOW... the style… the quality… just everything is top notch. 

Definitely support them. Get a fun box or gift a box this holiday season and know you are contributing to a great cause! 

#sponsored #blindresearch #blindchallenge #mysterybox #funbox #unboxing #fungiftidea #giftideasforchristmas #unbox #blindfolded 

Video Description: Tara is sitting at a coffee table unboxing a box from the Shop Blind Challenge by Two Blind Brothers. She first takes out a tote bag and stuffed guide dog with braille in its ear, then a t-shirt with braille on the hem, and a candle.

𝓗𝓪𝓿𝓮 you heard of Morpheus8? It’s an advanced needling treatment. So when we age, our skin begins to lose elasticity and with that comes wrinkles, lines, and a sagging appearance. Morpheus8 stimulates collagen production to tighten and smooth those wrinkles on your face and body. 🙌🏼

So I’ve partnered with @madaviaesthetics and had my first of three treatments. My experience was wonderful. First, we sat down and had a consultation. I can’t wait to see the results. Keep an eye on my stories in the next few weeks to see. They are in beautiful Beverly Hills and have a lovely menu of treatments such as peels, hydra facials and more and you can use my CODE Tara20 for 20% off.

Hellooo smooth skin! Do you take good care of your skin? I admit, I’m guilty of not taking the greatest care of my skin in my younger sun-loving days. I started changing all of that about 5 years ago… because… I started seeing it change and not for the better. 🙈

I’m beyonnnd excited for the opportunity to partner with @lifelineskincare to help improve my skin texture and over all appearance. 

They’re a bio-tech company and have access to the most cutting-edge technology. Yes please!

ISCO holds the global patent to create ethical stem cell which no one else in the world has access to this particular technology. Stem cells are the building blocks of life and are responsible for repairing our bodies and the healing process. Without stem cells, no life would ever be possible, nor would we be able to heal and repair our bodies after an injury. Stem cell extracts contain thousands of peptides and growth factors to increase collagen and elastin, production in your skin. 

Lifeline Stem Cell and Targeted Molecule Technology products are proven to speed the production of new skin cells, regulate collagen and elastin production. Improve skin firmness and elasticity, thickness, skin tone, and brightness enhancing the skin’s healing and repair process. 

I have a code right now for 50% off (GERARD50), which is incredible considering what is in this skincare line. I’ve been using the toner, exfoliator, aqueous, moisturizer and neck firming cream and my skin feels so clean, smooth and healthier. 

LOVE YOUR SKIN. 😘😘

Your makeup routine doesn’t actually start with makeup. Prepping your skin before doing your makeup is THE FIRST STEP! By doing so, you will create a more glowy and smoother look and feel for your skin once you apply your makeup. 

In this tutorial, you’ll see what I like to do pre makeup and you’ll see my FIVE FUN TIPS FOR FAAABULOUS MAKEUP!

TIP 1
Firstly, exfoliate exfoliate exfoliate. This will make your skin more smooth and cleanse your face of any dead skin cells that may be clogging your pores. 

TIP 2
Secondly, brightening toner. It helps to calm and protect the skin. 

TIP 3
Then add the eye firming complex, so it appears you’ve had plenty of beauty sleep when maybe you didn’t. 😘

TIP 4
After, advanced aqueous treatment for that serum and hydration. 

TIP 5
Lastly, the advanced recovery complex to moisturize and give a dewy look. 

THENNNNN YOU GET TO DO THAT MAKEUP OF YOURS! Et voilà! Fun and FABULOUS!

See this charming little dress Vienna is wearing? So there’s a story behind it. 

It’s always been a dream of mine to have a daughter and when I was a teenager and thrift shopping, I saw the cutest white eyelet dress for a little girl and I bought it in hopes of putting it on my little girl one day. 

I’ve had this dress now for nearly 25 years… it survived the struggle to have a successful pregnancy, it survived the almost loss of hope of ever using it, it survived our burglaries and many other crazy circumstances, but today my friends… I finally got to put that dress on my precious baby and it meant everything to me. 🥹

Never lose hope… even when it seems there is no other way, hold on to that hope.
